Package: bemudex
Version: 2.0.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ffmpeg, python3, libwebkit2gtk-4.0-37 | libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0
Maintainer: Vishrut Gundaji <vishrutgundaji@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/vish-1109/Bemudex
Description: A modern desktop media downloader powered by yt-dlp and FFmpeg
 Bemudex is a modern desktop media downloader powered by yt-dlp and FFmpeg.
 Built for Linux desktop environments with a modern, lightweight interface.
 .
 Features include high-quality video and audio downloads, playlist support,
 metadata embedding, thumbnail embedding, and a self-updating yt-dlp engine.
